The sum of the \(y\)-coordinates of all intersection points is:
\[0 + \frac{1}{34} + \frac{-1 + \sqrt{273}}{68} + \frac{-1 - \sqrt{273}}{68} = \frac{1}{34} + \frac{-1 + \sqrt{273} - 1 - \sqrt{273}}{68} = \frac{1}{34} + \frac{-2}{68} = \frac{1}{34} - \frac{1}{34} = 0\]
